story: Pwnky, a creature from the City of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Light green eyes  eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Mechanic mouth  mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Sad ear ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Yellow hair  hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Vikings hat hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Horns, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with City, Light green eyes , Mechanic body, Mechanic mouth , Sad ear, Yellow hair , Vikings hat, Horns
